| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-2425 — Recovery Inhibition (thegentlemen)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 520dec41-89cd-5124-8ce8-382259b03a02"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
